1
00:00:02,887 --> 00:00:07,899
♪Do you know, our fingertips
are bound by one string♪

2
00:00:07,900 --> 00:00:12,499
♪Tied to an attachment
that blooms only to fade♪

3
00:00:12,500 --> 00:00:13,999
♪By your side once♪

4
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:17,074
♪I laughed with the world
wild and free♪

5
00:00:17,075 --> 00:00:21,049
♪Yet now there's no one
to carry the story on♪

6
00:00:21,050 --> 00:00:25,970
♪Do you know you are the one string
woven through my fate♪

7
00:00:25,987 --> 00:00:30,699
♪Coiled through the years,
where longing sharpens into pain's line♪

8
00:00:30,700 --> 00:00:35,261
♪If love is meant to fall
more wretched the fiercer its flight♪

9
00:00:35,262 --> 00:00:40,445
♪Yet I still came to answer your call♪

10
00:00:40,725 --> 00:00:43,086
=Shall We Dance=

11
00:00:43,087 --> 00:00:46,132
=Episode 13=

12
00:00:47,140 --> 00:00:48,139
Duanmu Zhi.

13
00:00:48,140 --> 00:00:49,340
This is all your fault.

14
00:00:49,580 --> 00:00:50,739
Xiao Man and I were just about

15
00:00:50,740 --> 00:00:52,300
to make up when you barged in.

16
00:00:52,420 --> 00:00:54,299
Now look, she's angry again.

17
00:00:54,300 --> 00:00:55,820
You deal with it yourself.

18
00:00:56,340 --> 00:00:57,620
At the time,

19
00:00:57,740 --> 00:00:59,259
I was only trying
to protect Your Majesty.

20
00:00:59,260 --> 00:01:00,659
Did I ask for your protection?

21
00:01:00,660 --> 00:01:01,660
You...

22
00:01:06,140 --> 00:01:07,619
The memorials have been sorted.

23
00:01:07,620 --> 00:01:09,100
Please review them.

24
00:01:12,580 --> 00:01:15,020
Give me that memorial.

25
00:01:22,980 --> 00:01:24,100
Xiao Man...

26
00:01:26,900 --> 00:01:28,020
Xiao Man.

27
00:01:29,620 --> 00:01:31,580
I've already been punished.

28
00:01:32,100 --> 00:01:33,580
I shall take my leave.

29
00:01:39,340 --> 00:01:40,500
What?

30
00:01:44,420 --> 00:01:45,580
I take my leave now!

31
00:01:46,820 --> 00:01:47,940
Xiao Man.

32
00:01:48,460 --> 00:01:50,900
I have something
very important to explain to you.

33
00:01:51,460 --> 00:01:52,860
Your Majesty did nothing wrong.

34
00:01:53,180 --> 00:01:55,060
You safety concerns the realm.

35
00:01:55,100 --> 00:01:57,019
You couldn't be certain
whether I'd betray you,

36
00:01:57,020 --> 00:01:58,899
so you made preparations in advance.

37
00:01:58,900 --> 00:02:00,260
It was the most prudent plan

38
00:02:00,300 --> 00:02:02,379
and the most
responsible choice for Great Qian.

39
00:02:02,380 --> 00:02:03,500
Xiao Man...

40
00:02:04,060 --> 00:02:05,740
What you just said

41
00:02:06,020 --> 00:02:08,540
was better than all the excuses
I spent all night preparing.

42
00:02:09,780 --> 00:02:11,700
Since you understand me so well,

43
00:02:11,820 --> 00:02:13,540
don't be angry anymore.

44
00:02:14,020 --> 00:02:15,820
I'm not angry with Your Majesty.

45
00:02:15,900 --> 00:02:17,299
Whatever duties Your Majesty assigns,

46
00:02:17,300 --> 00:02:19,380
I'll carry them out
with utmost diligence.

47
00:02:19,440 --> 00:02:21,339
I've never neglected my post
over personal feelings.

48
00:02:21,340 --> 00:02:22,560
And you say you're not angry?

49
00:02:22,560 --> 00:02:24,499
You won't talk to me,
you won't even look at me.

50
00:02:24,500 --> 00:02:26,060
I'm mad at Chu Ying.

51
00:02:31,740 --> 00:02:33,699
I chose to return to your side.

52
00:02:33,700 --> 00:02:35,820
That means
I chose the risks of serving you.

53
00:02:36,820 --> 00:02:37,619
I know

54
00:02:37,620 --> 00:02:39,539
that to survive
in the palace all these years,

55
00:02:39,540 --> 00:02:41,260
you had to guard against everyone.

56
00:02:41,820 --> 00:02:42,499
But...

57
00:02:42,500 --> 00:02:44,580
But not against you.

58
00:02:45,940 --> 00:02:47,060
I didn't.

59
00:02:49,740 --> 00:02:50,900
If you don't believe me, look.

60
00:02:52,700 --> 00:02:53,820
No!

61
00:02:59,060 --> 00:03:01,940
This arrow is made of glutinous rice.

62
00:03:02,380 --> 00:03:04,820
The arrows aimed at you last night
were all like this.

63
00:03:04,940 --> 00:03:06,700
I've been meaning to explain.

64
00:03:06,980 --> 00:03:08,860
I never intended to hurt you.

65
00:03:09,860 --> 00:03:11,140
Rice arrows?

66
00:03:11,700 --> 00:03:12,820
Yes.

67
00:03:12,860 --> 00:03:14,220
Have you forgotten?

68
00:03:15,220 --> 00:03:17,500
I learned this trick that scares
but doesn't harm

69
00:03:18,220 --> 00:03:21,220
from you three years ago.

70
00:03:25,200 --> 00:03:29,857
(Three years ago,
8th Year of Hongzheng Reign)

71
00:04:05,260 --> 00:04:05,939
Brother,

72
00:04:05,940 --> 00:04:07,980
am I really that bad with the sword?

73
00:04:09,300 --> 00:04:10,179
Sister,

74
00:04:10,180 --> 00:04:13,379
you might not have the talent

75
00:04:13,380 --> 00:04:15,540
for refined weapons

76
00:04:15,860 --> 00:04:17,380
like bows and longswords.

77
00:04:17,460 --> 00:04:18,980
Just tell her the truth.

78
00:04:19,060 --> 00:04:21,700
Use the same words
your mother used on you.

79
00:04:26,580 --> 00:04:28,019
Your swordsmanship

80
00:04:28,020 --> 00:04:29,699
is so awful it makes me sick.

81
00:04:29,700 --> 00:04:30,619
Keep practising.

82
00:04:30,620 --> 00:04:32,300
Improve, or face military punishment!

83
00:04:33,540 --> 00:04:34,660
Mujun,

84
00:04:35,540 --> 00:04:37,140
a letter from the young emperor.

85
00:04:41,180 --> 00:04:42,420
Train first.

86
00:04:42,620 --> 00:04:43,540
Yes.

87
00:04:45,100 --> 00:04:45,859
Sister,

88
00:04:45,860 --> 00:04:46,539
for you,

89
00:04:46,540 --> 00:04:48,979
you could try weapons
like a spear or a lance.

90
00:04:48,980 --> 00:04:49,859
For you,

91
00:04:49,860 --> 00:04:51,259
they'd count as agile and manageable.

92
00:04:51,260 --> 00:04:52,420
Pick one.

93
00:04:56,660 --> 00:04:57,179
Sister,

94
00:04:57,180 --> 00:04:58,899
heavy weapons like these

95
00:04:58,900 --> 00:05:01,140
don't really suit a young lady like you.

96
00:05:04,860 --> 00:05:06,540
Why don't you choose another weapon?

97
00:05:16,540 --> 00:05:17,459
Uncle,

98
00:05:17,460 --> 00:05:18,580
Brother,

99
00:05:18,620 --> 00:05:20,180
may I read the letter now?

100
00:05:22,580 --> 00:05:23,700
Alright.

101
00:05:29,540 --> 00:05:31,140
Mu Yu, come.

102
00:05:31,820 --> 00:05:32,779
Come inside with me.

103
00:05:32,780 --> 00:05:33,899
The matter is important.

104
00:05:33,900 --> 00:05:34,860
Alright.

105
00:05:37,100 --> 00:05:39,300
Write a few
pleasing words to the emperor.

106
00:05:51,260 --> 00:05:52,059
Uncle,

107
00:05:52,060 --> 00:05:54,180
have you checked
the contents of the letter?

108
00:05:54,220 --> 00:05:55,460
I have.

109
00:05:55,740 --> 00:05:56,860
Nothing unusual.

110
00:05:59,140 --> 00:06:00,260
Now, to business.

111
00:06:01,020 --> 00:06:02,819
At past Ploughing Ceremonies,

112
00:06:02,820 --> 00:06:05,020
the young emperor was
always guarded closely.

113
00:06:05,580 --> 00:06:07,620
But this year, to avoid crowds

114
00:06:07,820 --> 00:06:09,059
disrupting the fields,

115
00:06:09,060 --> 00:06:10,820
I've withdrawn the guards.

116
00:06:10,940 --> 00:06:12,300
As for what to do,

117
00:06:12,637 --> 00:06:14,100
I'm sure you understand.

118
00:06:14,500 --> 00:06:15,620
I do.

119
00:06:15,660 --> 00:06:17,100
We'll use this chance

120
00:06:17,420 --> 00:06:18,980
to kill the young emperor.

121
00:06:45,075 --> 00:06:46,195
(Chu Ying...)

122
00:06:46,900 --> 00:06:48,340
(Are you safe?)

123
00:06:59,740 --> 00:07:00,860
Xiao Man...

124
00:07:01,740 --> 00:07:03,020
Are you safe?

125
00:08:01,740 --> 00:08:02,499
Assassins!

126
00:08:02,500 --> 00:08:03,380
Rice arrow...

127
00:08:03,500 --> 00:08:04,380
Quick!

128
00:08:06,820 --> 00:08:07,540
Stop!

129
00:08:07,780 --> 00:08:08,459
But,

130
00:08:08,460 --> 00:08:09,179
Your Majesty...

131
00:08:09,180 --> 00:08:10,860
I said stop, so stop.

132
00:08:11,300 --> 00:08:12,420
Stand down.

133
00:08:12,820 --> 00:08:13,940
Yes.

134
00:08:14,300 --> 00:08:15,140
Move.

135
00:08:17,660 --> 00:08:18,899
(Do not attend the ceremony.)

136
00:08:18,900 --> 00:08:20,020
(Danger.)

137
00:08:36,020 --> 00:08:36,739
Though at the time,

138
00:08:36,740 --> 00:08:39,020
I didn't see your face very clearly,

139
00:08:39,540 --> 00:08:40,940
I was certain

140
00:08:41,220 --> 00:08:43,340
the masked figure
who passed me that warning

141
00:08:43,780 --> 00:08:44,900
was you.

142
00:08:47,340 --> 00:08:48,219
And I

143
00:08:48,220 --> 00:08:50,940
was certain that I could never harm you.

144
00:08:51,140 --> 00:08:53,060
Just aiming an arrow at you

145
00:08:53,220 --> 00:08:55,420
was enough to make my heart tremble.

146
00:09:01,140 --> 00:09:02,580
Later, I found out

147
00:09:02,940 --> 00:09:04,219
that at the Ploughing Ceremony,

148
00:09:04,220 --> 00:09:05,660
the one who tried to kill me

149
00:09:07,380 --> 00:09:09,020
might've been Jia Yi.

150
00:09:11,340 --> 00:09:12,580
Honestly,

151
00:09:13,980 --> 00:09:15,940
learning that a loved one
tried to kill me

152
00:09:16,900 --> 00:09:19,140
felt like knives in my heart.

153
00:09:19,620 --> 00:09:22,660
Your godfather has been by your side
since you were six.

154
00:09:23,060 --> 00:09:25,860
Back then, we hadn't even met yet.

155
00:09:26,900 --> 00:09:28,020
That's right.

156
00:09:29,260 --> 00:09:31,820
He was the one
who raised me at his side.

157
00:09:33,340 --> 00:09:35,140
But he's not the same now.

158
00:09:35,980 --> 00:09:37,100
Xiao Man...

159
00:09:37,700 --> 00:09:39,420
What was Jia Yi's connection

160
00:09:40,020 --> 00:09:41,900
with the Zhen clan?

161
00:09:43,700 --> 00:09:45,580
Was he from the Zhen clan?

162
00:09:46,700 --> 00:09:47,940
Do you know

163
00:09:48,100 --> 00:09:50,420
what it means to have
a whole clan executed?

164
00:09:53,860 --> 00:09:54,980
An

165
00:09:55,620 --> 00:09:56,740
entire

166
00:09:57,100 --> 00:09:58,220
clan

167
00:09:58,780 --> 00:09:59,900
executed.

168
00:10:19,900 --> 00:10:21,380
Has His Majesty

169
00:10:22,020 --> 00:10:24,500
begun to suspect me?

170
00:10:24,775 --> 00:10:25,895
Uncle,

171
00:10:26,340 --> 00:10:27,219
Chu Ying has already

172
00:10:27,220 --> 00:10:29,059
agreed to clear the Zhen clan's name.

173
00:10:29,060 --> 00:10:30,139
Your plan

174
00:10:30,140 --> 00:10:31,740
can stop here.

175
00:10:32,740 --> 00:10:33,860
Xiao Man...

176
00:10:38,860 --> 00:10:41,940
That is absolutely impossible.

177
00:10:43,780 --> 00:10:46,219
I won't stop
just because their case is overturned.

178
00:10:46,220 --> 00:10:48,260
Nor will Mu Yu.

179
00:10:51,020 --> 00:10:52,140
However,

180
00:10:52,740 --> 00:10:55,460
I no longer want his life.

181
00:10:57,660 --> 00:10:59,340
What I want...

182
00:11:01,340 --> 00:11:04,420
is to seize the throne!
